posting_body: ['416 111th Street Court East, Tacoma, WA 98445', 'Monterra Apartments in Tacoma are conveniently located in the South neighborhood of Tacoma.', "With restaurants within walking distance, and shopping, schools, and parks nearby, you'll always find something to keep you busy at Monterra.", 'JBLM and the Tacoma waterfront are just a short drive away from the community.', 'Apartment Features:', 'Large Walk-In Closets', 'Vaulted Ceilings On Top Floor Units', 'Spacious Breakfast Bars', 'Full-Size Washer/Dryer', 'Walk-In Pantry', 'Extra Storage', 'Community Features:', 'Translation Service Available', 'Indoor Pool, Spa & Sauna', 'Lavish Cabana', 'Fitness Center', 'Covered Parking Available', 'Flexible Monthly Payments with Flex Rent', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
